<pre><code class="language-python">if keys[pygame.K_RIGHT]:
    velocity_x += ACCEL
ship_x += int(velocity_x)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> the velocity is never capped at a maximum.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code (add the speed limit):</strong></p>
