<h2>4 · Explain Your Lesson Code 🎥</h2>
<p>In today's live lesson you wrote your own ship-with-feel code. Now explain it. Record a short phone video. You may show your ship running while you talk. Try to use these words: <strong>velocity</strong>, <strong>acceleration</strong>, <strong>friction</strong>, <strong>max speed</strong>, <strong>Shift</strong>.</p>
<blockquote>
<ol>
<li>Show your ship flying slowly, then hold Shift and fly fast.</li>
<li>Let go of the keys and show the ship coasting to a stop.</li>
<li>Point to your friction line and say what 0.85 does.</li>
<li>Explain how your code stops the ship going past the max speed.</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
